business_context: Food deliver system is a platform that facilitates the delivery of food from restaurants to customers. It connects users with various food providers and manages the logistics of food delivery.

suggested_features.name: Order Tracking
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to track the status and location of their food delivery in real-time

suggested_features.name: Restaurant Listing
suggested_features.description: Provides a comprehensive list of restaurants available on the platform, including menus and ratings

suggested_features.name: Estimated Delivery Time
suggested_features.description: Informs customers about the estimated time of delivery for their orders

suggested_features.name: Order History
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to view their past orders and reorder items easily

suggested_features.name: Multiple Payment Options
suggested_features.description: Supports various payment methods including credit card, debit card, mobile wallets, and cash on delivery

suggested_features.name: Customer Reviews
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to leave reviews and ratings for restaurants and delivery personnel
